survey.music_making: When I was younger, I use to be a pretty good pianist. I passed all 8 levels of the Royal School of Music exams, and Nyssma. Every year, our piano school would hold a piano recital where all students performed.
survey.activities: I usually listen to music while driving or commuting via public transport.
survey.other_genres: Korean kpop music and Chinese music
survey.habit_change: No, I am pretty consistent with the type of music I've always liked over the years.
survey.habits: I sometimes add new songs that I discover from new movies or shows. I shazaam the song and then add it to my Spotify playlist.
